  "title": "BRAND MARKETING AMBASSADOR (Entry level | Training provided)",
  "description": "<p>Ready to kick-start your career—or feeling stuck trying to land your first role? Don’t stress, we’ve got you covered!</p><p>Whether you’ve just graduated or are eager to break into the world of Marketing, we’re always on the lookout for fresh talent. No experience? Totally fine. All we ask is a positive attitude and a strong desire to learn.</p><p></p><p>✨ <strong>WHO WE ARE</strong> ✨</p><p>We’re a fast-growing, dynamic marketing organisation based in Singapore, and we’re building an energetic team of passionate individuals.</p><p>Our mission is simple: help brands grow and connect with people in meaningful ways—and we’d love for you to be part of that journey.</p><p></p><p>🔖 <strong>WHAT YOU’LL DO</strong> 🔖</p><p>* Understand customer needs and market trends</p><p>* Learn the ins and outs of the brands we represent</p><p>* Engage with clients through face-to-face interactions</p><p>* Take ownership of campaigns and bring creative ideas to life</p><p></p><p>🚀 <strong>WHAT YOU’LL GET</strong> 🚀</p><p>* Real career growth opportunities—clear progression, not empty promises</p><p>* A fun, supportive, and high-energy team that’s got your back every step of the way 🎉</p><p></p><p>Ready to take the leap? Let’s make great things happen together. <strong>JOIN US TODAY!</strong> ⭐️</p><p></p>",
